{
  "stem": "753.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you can imagine living in a house like this where they were constantly singing, we don't want Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Out with them, out with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a certain song that they were singing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these were young punks that were never good for anything, and now they've got these beautiful positions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew that our days are numbered in that apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what was surprising, people that seemed our friends, that seemed at least our acquaintances, that were not Jewish-- when we would go down the stairs or in the elevator, they never talked to us.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They looked away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They looked down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They looked up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was like some-- we were-- we had a plague, or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We never heard a good word.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, this is-- will be over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And and don't worry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we're on your side-- never.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was-- our experience was not benevolent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we thought that we are liked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not yet.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just felt there is a excitement, that our life is not anymore as it used to be, that-- my parents don't care what I do, where I go.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a chaos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would meet with some friends who were not going to school either [SIGHS] in my house or in their house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And slowly, they were, like, disappearing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know where-- I had my best friend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She left with her family to Banja Luka, which is in Bosnia, with her parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were just leaving, coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody was smart to say, you know what, if we follow this, that will help.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody was doing his own thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But let me tell you what really changed fast our situation.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
